        "subject": "Young man in a blue shirt studying at a desk, writing in a notebook next to an open laptop.",
        "elements": ["bright indoor lighting", "desk environment"],
        "text_labels": [
          "スキマ時間で",
          "{argument name=\"education goal\" default=\"最短合格！\"}",
          "オンライン資格講座",
          "スマホで完結",
          "効率学習で差がつく！",
          "今だけ！ 受講料 20%OFF"
